\f0\b\fs36 \cf2 ME
\f1\b0\fs24 \
\
\
What do you do when you get a gift you don\'92t want or ask for. \'a0\
\
There\'92s a chance you may not get what you want on Christmas. \'a0\
\
Don\'92t give up, give up!!!\
\
When you Give Up to God what your are struggling with He replaces it with something better. \'a0\
\
\
Receive favor and give up fear\
Receive faith and give up doubt/sight\
Receive focus and give up expectations\'a0\
\
Don\'92t give up, give up!\
\
When you give it to God something happens and He replaces it with something better. \'a0\
\
\
\
\
