\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Is there something here about Joseph\'92s expectation for her to be a virgin?\uc0\u8232 \
\ls6\ilvl2\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9642 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
