\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Some of you are going to have to give up the expectations of those around you, maybe even those who love you most and know you best.\uc0\u8232 \
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\partightenfactor0
